race.description: Darling View Thoroughbreds - Dare To Dream Hcp
race.comment: ROMMEL'S GODDESS (5) Has been narrowly beaten her past two in this grade and now steps out to 1400m again. That trip is the query, though she draws the inside and she has gone to another level this time in. Drops slightly in weight here and she can go one better. SUPERFLUOUS (6) may have found the 1500m journey a bridge too far last time out when beaten 2L. He was trending the right way prior to that event and will find this a little easier than what he took on last start. May get back in the run but he looks poised to strike. ON PATROL (2) only just missed when sitting on the speed at Ascot last time out. Drawn out again here, but Parnham has options and he'll be at peak fitness here. Can feature again. MONTE TREMEZZO (10) is better than we saw last time out and can improve with the Blinkers on first time today. SHOW THE WAY (11) wasn't beaten far last time out and hits third third-up. Watch or him flying late in the race.
